@node "BATTLE SQUADRON"
BATTLE SQUADRON

Type "ELECTRONIC" on the intro to call up the game options editor.

Type in "CASTOR" during play- the screen will flash green indicating
the cheat mode is active.  Both ships are now invincible.  Pressing 'F6' -
'F10' will select different types of weapons.  'F1' - 'F5' will alter their
power.
@endnode
@node "BATTLE VALLEY"
BATTLE VALLEY

Type "ROGER MELLIE THE MAN ON THE TELE" activates infinite lives cheat.
@endnode
@node "BEACH VOLLEY"
BEACH VOLLEY

Type "DADDYBRACEY" (NOTE: May have a space like "DADDY BRACEY") to activate
the level skip option.  The screen should flash.  Press 'F1' to skip levels.  
@endnode
@node "BEAST BUSTERS"
BEAST BUSTERS

If you pause the game you can still move the crosshair around!
@endnode
@node "BEAVERS"
BEAVERS

On the title screen, type "ZEGOOLI" to start at level 8 or type "MRCLINK"
to start at level 15.  During play, type "BIGGIGBIB" and then press 'F2' to
skip levels and use the 'SPACE BAR' to select any position in the level.
@endnode        
@node "BETTER DEAD THAN ALIEN"
BETTER DEAD THAN ALIEN

Typing "CHAMP" then pressing "HELP" will show you the cheats available.

  Keys for cheating:   'F1' - Scatterbolts     'F6' - Neutron Bomb
                       'F2' - Multi Fire       'F7' - Clone Ship
                       'F3' - Auto Repeat      'F8' - Shield
                       'F4' - Armour Missles   'F9' - Skip Level
                       'F5' - Stun             'F10' - Extra Power Bars

If the passwords are extended into the names of the programmers, "ELVIE" and
"CHAMPIE", the program states that the "Supercheat" has been entered.  If
anyone finds out just exactly what this does, drop me a line, eh?

