@node "BEVERLY HILLS COP"
BEVERLY HILLS COP

Click past the high score screen onto the select difficulty page.  Type
"MELLIE" and you will be able to access all the games.
@endnode
@node "BEYOND THE GATES"
BEYOND THE GATES

Entering "THE END OF TIME DRAWS NEAR"  will call up a full character editor
that allows you to change your stats and add any item to your inventory.
@endnode
@node "BIG RUN"
BIG RUN

While playing, pause the game and move your joystick left, right, down, up,
up, left, down, and right.  Note that you have to center the stick after
every move.  Now the screen should flicker and you'll be the proud owner of
infinite credits.
@endnode
