@node "BUNNY BRICKS"
BUNNY BRICKS

To skip levels, hold down 'ALT', 'CTRL', 'R SHIFT', and 'N'.  For extra balls,
hold 'ALT', CTRL', 'R SHIFT', and 'L'.  To skip sections, hold 'ALT', 'CTRL',
'R SHIFT', 'T' and a number '1' - '5'.  To increase playability, hold down
'L AMIGA', 'R AMIGA', and 'CTRL' (reset your amiga).
@endnode
        